cs.HC, cs.SE, cs.CV, cs.PL, cs.SD 

This paper focuses on the automated verification of GUI design in mobile apps, which is a problem related to human-computer interaction (HCI) and software engineering (SE). Therefore, cs.HC and cs.SE are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses computer vision techniques to identify errors, which suggests that cs.CV is a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the tool, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and software development (cs.SD).
